config STEPPER
	bool "Stepper Motor Driver"
	depends on GPIO
	help
	  Enable stepper motor driver for A4988/DRV8825 modules.
	  Supports velocity control with automatic degrees/s to microstep conversion.
	  Uses Zephyr timers for precise step pulse generation.